@startuml
title City-Scale Digital Twin: Level 0 DFD (Context Diagram)

skinparam actor {
  FontSize 12
  BorderColor #C2185B
  BackgroundColor #FCE4EC
  FontColor #880E4F
}

skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #1565C0
  BorderThickness 2
  FontSize 14
  BackgroundColor #BBDEFB
  FontColor #0D47A1
}

actor "IoT Sensors &\nSimulator" as Sensors
actor "City Managers &\nPlanners" as CityAdmin
actor "QA Engineers" as QA
actor "DevOps\nEngineers" as DevOps
actor "System\nAdministrators" as Admins

rectangle "City-Scale Digital Twin\nIoT Platform" as System

' Data Flows
Sensors -->|Real-time Sensor Data\n(MQTT)| System : "IoT Data Stream"
System -->|City Insights\nAlerts & Reports| CityAdmin : "Actionable Intelligence"
CityAdmin -->|User Commands\nQueries & Configurations| System : "User Requests"

System -->|Test Commands\nTest Execution| QA : "Testing Interface"
QA -->|Test Reports\nResults & Logs| System : "Test Feedback"

System -->|Performance Metrics\nHealth Status| DevOps : "Monitoring Data"
DevOps -->|Optimization Requests\nConfiguration Changes| System : "DevOps Commands"

System -->|System Status\nAudit Logs| Admins : "Administration Data"
Admins -->|Access Control\nSecurity Policies| System : "Admin Commands"

note right of System
  Centralized IoT Data Platform
  - Real-time data ingestion from 12 sensor types
  - REST API for data retrieval and management
  - Web UI for visualization and analytics
  - Testing and monitoring capabilities
  - Multi-user support with role-based access
end note

@enduml